name: A. HQ9+
statement:
HQ9+ is a joke programming language which has only four one-character
instructions: "" prints "", "" prints the source code of the program
itself, "" prints the lyrics of "99 Bottles of Beer" song, "" increments
the value stored in the internal accumulator.Instructions "" and "" are
case-sensitive and must be uppercase. The characters of the program
which are not instructions are ignored.You are given a program written
in HQ9+. You have to figure out whether executing this program will
produce any output.
